cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.PL

The paper discusses the challenges and patterns for migrating Blockchain platforms, which involves data management, smart contract representations, and transaction fees. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DB (Databases), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
